title: Trace Route
description: Trace Route was the final project for my CS372 Intro to Computer Networks class. It involved creating an implementation of a ping function and then using that ping function to create a trace route function.

title: Fighting Fighters
description: Fighting Fighters is the group final project for my CS290 Web Development class. It's a 1v1 card fighting game with multiple classes to choose from.

title: Reverse Temps
description: Reverse Temps was the portfolio project for my CS271 Computer Architecture and Assembly Language class. It reads a list of temperatures from a -delimited file, stores them in memory, and prints them out in the reverse order. The code makes use of the Irvine32 library.
